==English==
=== Noun ===

# In general, a prefabricated subassembly, interchangeable with its sibling subassemblies, which can be easily installed in or removed from a larger mechanism, and whose prefabrication obviates the need to handle its constituent parts individually. Specific examples of the general principle follow.
## The case which holds the explosive charge (for example, gunpowder) and primer for a round of ammunition.
## The aforementioned case and its bullet, together as one unit.
## A vessel which contains the ink or toner for a computer printer and can be easily replaced with another.
## A magnetic tape data storage device, for example an audio cassette, consisting of reels for the tape and a housing to hold them in correct position.
# (obsolete) a small paper package, e.g. in an old book about making printer's type: ''After all the type has been cast: "The Boy will paper up each sort in a cartridge by itself"''.

